         <abstract>
            <p>Explicit inverses and condition numbers of two test-circulants with first rows {a, a + h, ⋯, a + (n - 1)h} and {a, ah, ⋯, ah&lt;sup&gt;n-1&lt;/sup&gt;} respectively are given in terms of the parameters defining the circulants.</p>
